<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٢٦٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4846">عَمْرُو بْنُ عَاصِمٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6739">هَمَّامٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«قُلْتُ لِأَنَسٍ: أَكَانَتِ الْمُصَافَحَةُ فِي أَصْحَابِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>